<plot>A parody-spoof about corruption and immorality in the Honk Kong Police late during the British occupation. Ray Lui stars as the new hotshot cop, constantly challenged by his wannabe rivals, who all aspire to impress and thus inherit the right to take over from the soon-to-retire senior detective, played by Kent Cheng.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?665203</url></doc>
